      "message": "[Medium] Line 703: 🟡 Suggestions - setZoomRatio posts every pinch update to the camera handler without coalescing. A pinch gesture can generate many UI events faster than Camera2 can apply repeating requests, causing a backlog of stale zoom requests and visible latency. Coalesce updates by keeping only the latest requested ratio, or remove pending zoom-update runnables before posting a new one.\n\n```suggestion\n// Store latestZoomRatio on VideoParams and post at most one pending update;\n// when the runnable executes, read the latest value and apply a single repeating request.\n```",
