      "message": "[Medium] Line 135: 🟡 Suggestions - attach() installs a listener that returns true for every touch, even when scale \u003d\u003d 1f and the gesture is just a normal tap/scroll. Since ParticipantsContainerView enables this on active call tiles, the video surface can swallow touches that parent views may rely on for participant focus, controls, or accessibility behavior. Only consume events when a zoom gesture is in progress or the view is zoomed/pannable; otherwise let the event bubble.\n\n```suggestion\nval consumed \u003d scaleDetector.isInProgress || scale \u003e minScale || ev.pointerCount \u003e 1\nif (ev.actionMasked \u003d\u003d MotionEvent.ACTION_UP \u0026\u0026 consumed) {\n    v.performClick()\n}\nconsumed\n```",
